{"text":"Welcome to Nadir!

This datapack expands enchanting by rebalancing vanilla enchantments, adding new ones, and reworking the Enchanting Table.

Craft this book anytime by combining Enchanted Book + Blaze Powder."}

{"text":"Enchanting Table

Nadir reinvents the Enchanting Table interaction. There is no GUI - instead, right-clicking brings up a text menu.

You can enchant items or dismantle the table (owner only)."}
